\chi^2 = \sum_{i=1}^{n} \frac{(O_i - E_i)^2}{E_i}
E_i=\frac{N}{n}
i
\chi^2 = \sum_{i=1}^{n} \frac{(O_i - \frac{N}{n})^2}{\frac{N}{n}}
= \frac{n}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{n} (O_i - \frac{N}{n})^2
= \frac{n}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{n} (\frac{1}{n})^2(nO_i - N)^2
= \frac{1}{nN}\sum_{i=1}^{n} (nO_i - N)^2
\chi^2_{worst} = \frac{1}{nN}[(nN - N)^2 + (n-1)(-N)^2]
= \frac{N}{n}[(n - 1)^2 + (n-1)]
= \frac{N}{n}[n^2 -n]
= N(n-1)
\frac{\chi^2}{\chi^2_{worst}}
